PrecisAuthority to enter into AGREEMENTS which provide for the granting of funds to non-government environmental organizations (such as Nature Trust, Ducks Unlimited, etc.) who undertake to apply those funds towards the acquisition or leasing of lands in British Columbia for the long-term conservation and management of waterfowl habitats (wetlands).
